Package com.complexible.stardog.jena

Provides classes for Stardog-Jena integration.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
JenaSesameUtils Utility methods for converting between the Jena and Sesame APIs
SDJenaFactory Factory for obtaining instances of the Jena framework core, specifically Models and Datasets, which are backed by Stardog.
StardogModelAssembler An assembler implementation to build a Stardog model from an assembler description in RDF.
StardogModelAssembler.OWL2Profile URIs for OWL 2 profiles as defined by W3C.
StardogModelAssembler.Vocabulary Stardog assembler vocabulary.
